    <h1 class="title topictitle1" id="ariaid-title1">TERMA Radar</h1>

    
    <div class="body"><p class="shortdesc">The <em class="ph i">TERMA Radar</em> uses electro magnetic waves to discover objects.</p>

        <p class="p">The <em class="ph i">Terma Radar Antenna</em> is a rotating mechanical device that follows the principle
            of a gearbox which features a drive shaft for the scanner, a motor, a gear, encoder
            assembly and a junction box for all electrical connections.</p>

        <div class="fig fignone" id="comp_terma_radar__TERMA_principle_of_gearbox"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 1. </span>TERMA Principle of Gearbox</span>
            
            <img class="image" src="../../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-050100000-A-D2714-06023-A-01-1.jpg" />
        </div>

        <div class="fig fignone" id="comp_terma_radar__TERMA_Radar_Dimensions"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 2. </span>TERMA Radar Dimensions</span>
            
            <img class="image" src="../../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-050100000-A-D2714-06024-A-01-1.jpg" />
        </div>

        <p class="p">The full TERMA configuration is shown in <a class="xref" href="#comp_terma_radar__Simplified_block_diagram">Figure 3</a> (for illustration purposes
            only). The actual physical setup does not include the <em class="ph i">Scanter Antenna Control Unit</em>
            frame. </p>

        <div class="fig fignone" id="comp_terma_radar__Simplified_block_diagram"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 3. </span>Simplified Block Diagram of TERMA Installation</span>
            
            <img class="image" src="../../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-050100000-A-D2714-06025-A-01-1.jpg" height="291" width="283" />
        </div>

        <div class="fig fignone" id="comp_terma_radar__TERMA_radar_mounted_on_tower"><span class="figcap"><span class="fig--title-label">Figure 4. </span>TERMA Radar Mounted on Tower</span>
            
            <img class="image" src="../../images/ICN-ACTA-AA-050100000-A-D2714-06026-A-01-1.jpg" />
        </div>

    </div>

